<item>
            <title>[LU-12523] Add jobid to rpctrace debug messages</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12523</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;All rpcs contain a jobid string in the ptlrpc_body. It is null if jobid_var is not enabled. Since a string is always available from the rpc and jobid can very useful in analyzing system activity, the jobid should included in the rpctrace debug messages.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
